  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00043', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設某消費者的預算限制方程式為4X+5Y=100，其中X和Y為財貨的消費數量，消費1單位X 財貨的機會成本為何？', '["0.8單位的Y財貨", "1.25單位的Y財貨", "4單位的Y財貨", "5單位的Y財貨"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00044', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設有一商品其供給彈性之絕對值大於需求彈性之絕對值，若政府決定對該項商品課稅，則實際 稅負主要由何者承受？', '["消費者", "生產者", "消費者和生產者承受比重相同", "取決於稅負是向消費者或生產者徵收"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00045', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設消費者的效用函數為U(X,Y)=X+Y，其中X和Y為財貨的消費數量，下列敘述何者正確？', '["此效用函數所代表的偏好不滿足完整性", "此效用函數所代表的偏好不滿足遞移性", "此效用函數所代表的偏好不滿足越多越好的特性", "此效用函數所代表的偏好不滿足嚴格凸性"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00046', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一廠商的生產函數為q=L0.5K1.5，其中q為生產量、L為勞動要素投入量、而K則為資本要素 投入量。有關此生產函數邊際產量（marginalproduct）之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["勞動的邊際產量遞增，資本的邊際產量遞增", "勞動的邊際產量遞增，資本的邊際產量遞減", "勞動的邊際產量遞減，資本的邊際產量遞增", "勞動的邊際產量遞減，資本的邊際產量遞減"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
